sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Browser (Templates)
    participant View as Django View
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open Create Note page
    UI->>View: GET /note/new/
    View-->>UI: Render note_form.html

    User->>UI: Submit note form
    UI->>View: POST /note/new/ (title, content)
    View->>View: Validate NoteForm
    View->>DB: INSERT Note
    DB-->>View: Note saved
    View-->>UI: Redirect to /
    UI-->>User: Notes list updated
